'''Bantay''' is a 4th class [[Philippine municipality|municipality]] in the [[Philippine province|province]] of [[Ilocos Sur province|Ilocos Sur]], [[Philippines]]. According to the [[2000]] census, it has a population of 30,519 people in 6,107 households.

